name: Ayra Ali
description: I am a student at the University of Waterloo pursuing Honours Co-op Chemistry/Biochemistry while I explore technology along with my adoration for writing. I am also a TEDx speaker, the Founder at Ehsaas, a Round Square attendee, a Gulf Debates winner, a competitive innovator and a writer, and I hope to help you find further opportunities to foster growth and creativity.
Provides direct access to admitted student for one hour
Clear program-specific queries, and general doubts
In-depth review of college essays (personal statements)
Direct access to successful college essays
Ideal for high school students who want comprehensive support

reviews.description: I really enjoyed this meeting, I thought she had some great expertise on the admissions process especially since she knows how to collaborate with students and to help them bring about a drastic improvement in their essays.
